blog.title: The Sturdy Nerdy Stitchery
blog.description:
What's the stitch? Nooo! Not Kim Possible! Stitch? Nooo! Not experiment 626! I'm talking about cross stitch because cross stitch, knitting, and all other stitch craft! I mean, that's what all the cool kids are into, right? I'm a Cool kid!
Check out my Etsy page for more cool stitchin stuff: Sturdy Nerdy Stitchery

body:
Big mood

LET ME CRY AND WHINE! I carelessly left a pile of knitting projects on the couch. A messy pile. I go to clean and tidy the couch….AND ONE PROJECT IS MISSING A NEEDLE! IT FELL OF THE SCARF AND I THINK THE COUCH ATE IT!

I AM FURIOUSLY DIGGING AROUND CUSHIONS AND DIGGING MY FAT HANDS INTO PLACES THAT MY FAT HANDS PROBABLY DONT FIT!

No no no no no! THIS CANT BE HAPPENING…WHAT IF IT’S TOO FAR INTO THE COUCH FOR ME TO REACH UNLESS I RISK INJURY?!

Augh!

summary: I like that the special showed some insights into the background characters life, such as more Tsunoda, Kabae’s kids, Tsubone...
body:
I like that the special showed some insights into the background characters life, such as more Tsunoda, Kabae’s kids, Tsubone actually not being a bitch, and even some Resasuke celebrating at the end.

My biggest complaint is where is Komiya and what is he doing for Christmas

He’s such a better character in the original show
